Privacy Policy<br>
This document sets out how we use, process and protect your personal data you give us when using this website and ABC Mobile OÜ services/products and other content. We act in our customers' interest and are transparent about the processing of your personal data.<br>
That means we are committed to protecting and safeguarding any personal data you give us. As an added bonus, it also tells you how to contact us if you have questions about your personal data. This one Privacy Policy applies to any kind of information we collect through our own website/apps, as well as through social media or our partners’ websites.<br>
We might amend the Privacy Policy from time to time. If you care about your privacy, visit this page regularly to know exactly where you stand. If we make changes to the Privacy Policy which will have an impact on you (e.g. if we intend to process your personal data for other purposes than communicated in the past in this Privacy Policy), we'll notify you of these changes before the new activities begin.<br>
The hard truth: Your use of this website and/or our services/products here constitute your consent to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you disagree with this Privacy Policy, you should discontinue using our services/products and this website.<br>
Any Information provided by you with which you can be identified when using this website and our services/products, will be used in accordance with this Privacy Policy. This Policy sets out the following:<br>
1. What information we collect<br>
2. How the information is used by us<br>
3. How do we store and maintain data<br>
4. Disclosure<br>
5. Cookies<br>
6. Your rights<br>
7. Contact details<br>
What information we collect<br>
The information collected by us is necessary to provide you with a service/product and/or to allow us to optimize our services/products. Such information can be collected when you use this website or when you use each of our services including our premium rate services and/or products.<br>
The information we collect may include:<br>
- Your name<br>
- Gender<br>
- Date/Time of birth (age)<br>
- Email address<br>
– Telephone number.<br>
In some cases, we may collect and process the following information (depending on the type of service and/or product): your habits (including harmful addictions); hobbies and fancies; food excesses; clothing, pastime preferences and etc.; the favorite music; sport and sporting performance; your skills and experiences; personality traits and personal skills; educational background; relationship status; place of living (city, country); professional occupation, place of work/study; fears; the favorite color, country, city and other preferences, likes and dislikes; general information about wellbeing (NOTE: We collect and use only general information about your health, excluding data on diagnosis, diseases, tests, mental state and other anamnesis data) and other general data.<br>
In addition to this, we also collect automatically information from your phone tablet/mobile device or other device you're using to access our website, services and/or products. This can include the IP address, data that identifies your mobile device, device-specific settings and characteristics, the browser you're using, app crashes, social network account, and other system activity, your language settings and location details. There are also situations when we receive information about you from others or automatically collect other information.<br>
Our premium rate service can store your mobile phone number, the number you dialed, the length and frequency of your calls. We also store information on any interactions via social media platforms or forums. In addition to that, you can provide us with feedback or ask for help with using our support service, which involves providing us with personal data.<br>
DISCLAMER: ALL INFORMATION AND/OR “ADVICES”, “TESTS RESULTS”, “PREDICTIONS” CONTAINED ON OUR WEBSITE, APPS, SERVICES/PRODUCTS ARE PROVIDED FOR ENTERTAINMENT PURPOSES ONLY, AND SHOULD NOT BE CONSTRUED AS MEDICAL, LEGAL, OR FINANCIAL ADVICE ON ANY SUBJECT MATTER. THE ABC MOBILE OÜ DISCLAIMS ALL LIABILITY IN REGARDS TO ACTIONS TAKEN OR NOT TAKEN BASED ON ANY OR ALL OF THE CONTENTS ON THIS WEBSITE. PLEASE NOTE THAT ABC MOBILE OÜ DOES NOT NECESSARILY ENDORSE, AND IS NOT RESPONSIBLE FOR, ANY THIRD-PARTY CONTENT THAT MAY BE ACCESSED THROUGH THIS WEBSITE.<br>
